Install Java 9 and CSP compilation on Ubuntu or Debian x64bits
#EDITED BY SHARILLAS


1-  apt-get update
2-  apt-get install sudo subversion tar python-software-properties software-properties-common
3-  apt-get update
4-  echo "deb http://ppa.launchpad.net/webupd8team/java/ubuntu trusty main" | tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/webupd8team-java.list
5-  echo "deb-src http://ppa.launchpad.net/webupd8team/java/ubuntu trusty main" | tee -a /etc/apt/sources.list.d/webupd8team-java.list
6-  apt-key adv --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com --recv-keys EEA14886
7-  apt-get remove --purge openjdk-*
8-  apt-get update
9-  apt-get install oracle-java6-installer
10- apt-get install oracle-java6-set-default
11- cd lib
12- mkdir cspsvn
13- cd cspsvn
14- svn co http://streamboard.tv/svn/CSP/trunk CSP-svn
15- apt-get install ant
16- cd CSP-svn
17- ant build
18- ant tar-app
19- cd dist
20- tar -zxvf cardservproxy.tar.gz
21- mv cardservproxy /usr/local/csp
22- cd /usr/local/csp
23- ./cardproxy.sh start
and again repeat command
24- ./cardproxy.sh start
Starting CardServProxy: [ OK ]
25- Browser= http://ip_do_server:8082  user:admin pass:secret

ACTUALIZAR O JAVA para a Ultima versão
26- ./cardproxy.sh stop
27- apt-get remove --purge oracle-java6-installer oracle-java6-set-default
28- apt-get remove --purge openjdk-*
29- apt-get update
30- apt-get install oracle-java9-installer oracle-java9-set-default
31- dizer "yes" aceito os termos do java e ENTER
32- ./cardproxy start
Starting CardServProxy: [ OK ]
25- Browser= http://ip_do_server:8082  user:admin pass:secret

Configurar o CSP com SSL ou seja em ves de http:ip_do_server:8082 fica https://ip_do_server:8082

26- ./cardproxy.sh stop
27- keytool -keystore csp_keystore -genkey -alias Cardservproxy -keyalg RSA -storepass mypassword123 -keypass mypassword123 -dname "cn=yourserver.dyndns.org" -validity 1000
mv csp_keystore /usr/local/csp/etc/
28- depois ir por winscp á pasta /usr/local/csp/config/proxy.xml e editar o ficheiro proxy.xml:
<ssl enabled="true">
<keystore password="mypassword123">etc/csp_keystore</keystore>
</ssl>
29- ./cardproxy.sh start
30- Browser= https://ip_do_server:8082 user:admin pass:secret
Ligação ao CSP segura encryptada por ssl
